5|$|Snake {{enters the}} {{facility}} via an air vent and locates the first <b>hostage,</b> DARPA Chief Donald Anderson. Anderson reveals that Metal Gear REX can be deactivated {{with a secret}} detonation override code, but dies of a heart attack. Colonel Campbell's niece Meryl Silverburgh, held <b>hostage</b> in an adjoining cell, helps Snake escape. Snake locates another <b>hostage,</b> ArmsTech president Kenneth Baker, but is confronted by FOXHOUND member Revolver Ocelot. Their gunfight is interrupted by a mysterious cyborg ninja who cuts off Ocelot's right hand. Baker briefs Snake on the Metal Gear project and advises him to contact Meryl, whom he gave a PAL card that might prevent the launch, but he too dies of a sudden heart attack.|$|E
